{"tid":2500950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"謝偉俊：稱天氣太熱或成煽惑不投票，促清晰界定","createTime":"2021-04-23T04:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T05:50:25.000Z","uid":278587,"like":47,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"15ce110c50be857b4ce7b8a153ba5dab5675ff47","tid":2500950,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2021/04/23/2776808_34f7f22b5e1857391b560d18380693e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2021%2F04%2F23%2F2776808_34f7f22b5e1857391b560d18380693e4.jpg&h=fe89d7ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府修改本港選舉制度，訂明任何人在選舉期間內，藉公開活動煽惑他人不投票、投白票或廢票，即屬犯法。<br />\n<br />\n議員謝偉俊在立法會相關法案委員會指出，天氣太熱太冷或有疫症也能叫人不要投票，即使有幾好的理由，也會成為煽惑，希望當局在法例中清晰界定。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯議員梁美芬說，「煽惑」需要有故意犯罪才能構成有關罪行，建議條文可清楚列明「任何人若意圖操控或破壞選舉而進行符合任何一項描述的公開活動」。<br />\n<br />\n律政司署理律政專員梅基發提到，條文清楚列明控方要證明有煽惑行為，控方有責任去清楚證明有煽惑意圖，罪行條文現時沒有要求控方要另外去證明一個特定意圖，例如破壞選舉。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰指出，任何方式的展示，包括動作姿勢等都可以成為煽惑，擔心出現「砌生豬肉」。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞表示，涉及刑事罪行，無論取證及舉證都要非常嚴謹，甚麼情況下構成煽惑或行為是有很高規格，在法庭才能被接納。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰又關注，若家人擔心院舍長者在選舉期間被送往票站投票或會取走長者身份證，質疑在現行法例下是否屬違法。當局稱，若動機是妨礙或阻礙長者投票，當然屬違犯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2776808/謝偉俊%3A稱天氣太熱或成煽惑不投票+促清晰界定\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2776808%2F%E8%AC%9D%E5%81%89%E4%BF%8A%253A%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E5%A4%AA%E7%86%B1%E6%88%96%E6%88%90%E7%85%BD%E6%83%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%2B%E4%BF%83%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%AE%9A&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=6d498e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2776808/謝偉俊%3A稱天氣太熱或成煽惑不投票+促清晰界定</a>"},{"pid":"0cf2f398b9f59270d8f1f4757cb3dbded6aff020","tid":2500950,"uid":156542,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"行去票站太遠 <br />\n天氣太熱<br />\n排隊太多人"},{"pid":"279015f7bcab12ac908d88393c3e322ff064deda","tid":2500950,"uid":107419,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"要屌你老母，所以唔得閒去投票。"},{"pid":"11c62ac0d03e5bd557adb59f1c81b31f6f7b25b2","tid":2500950,"uid":31237,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"要返工<br />\n投票？不了"},{"pid":"378c2af3aeb75204cf30025dc51120bfc4c3ece2","tid":2500950,"uid":308026,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"塊地好硬 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f51d3a01b7f54fbb5493f7609eb2e4ccb7e52d","tid":2500950,"uid":112416,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"11c62ac0d03e5bd557adb59f1c81b31f6f7b25b2","tid":2500950,"uid":31237,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"要返工<br />\n投票？不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"拉僱主？"},{"pid":"5abc197256366d119b15adcb97785b0b56e308ab","tid":2500950,"uid":1166,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"返工都可以犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96e9765f63207fa6332f607c262e205e610b702","tid":2500950,"uid":19640,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"亞爺話你犯法咪犯法囉，問咁多做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a23e9d3ade2a8e8865e261075d393497c9dc0f","tid":2500950,"uid":391165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:46:26.000Z","msg":"唔做選民=犯法"},{"pid":"29a6fc46510f0ce82d1c5c3af8605f93e4e4ed6e","tid":2500950,"uid":272652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:46:35.000Z","msg":"放假投票不了"},{"pid":"5a68